ou3

Class Route

  • java.lang.Object
    • ou3.Route

  • public class Route
extends java.lang.Object
    The Class Route, containing information used in the routingTables pertaining to how to get to an event. Will be bound to a specific Event by the ID, and know the distance there. Will also store information about which way to go to get there.
